^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So, Roberta, despite the horrible trump break you made 3S. Bidding is almost always better than passing. Dee's 3D is aggressive but I like it particularly at this vulnerability. She is not we are. Speaking of preempts, the worst seat to preempt in is 2nd seat. The reason being is you already know your right hand opponent doesn't have that good a hand, making it more likely partner has some values and you will be preempting partner. So, some people who are aggressive preempters in first and third seats are much more conservative in 2nd seat.|
