NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|In Roberta's case, she has 2 choices--double or 3S. With fewer points and a doubleton heart, double would be iffy. But because she has 16 points, she can correct to 3S, even though her suit is not ideal. The diamond holding is not the problem, the heart holding is. If your club suit and heart suit were reversed, she has a clear double. Personally, here I would double, double and correct to show the points, but 3S is reasonable as well.|
